WEBVTT

02:00:04.834 --> 02:00:06.793
Sir, sir... Please listen to me, sir.
-Hey Boka.

02:00:07.043 --> 02:00:07.834
You...

02:00:09.334 --> 02:00:10.001
Boka!

02:00:10.251 --> 02:00:11.584
He’s again showing that to me.

02:00:11.584 --> 02:00:13.209
Sir.. sir.. sir...
-Hey... I’ll kill you.

02:00:16.668 --> 02:00:17.043
Sir!

02:00:17.709 --> 02:00:19.751
South India is in riots all at once, sir.

02:00:20.709 --> 02:00:22.501
Already, four police stations
have been burned down, sir.

02:00:29.501 --> 02:00:33.084
And people are being brutally killed in cities like
Hyderabad, Chennai, Kochi, and Bengaluru, sir.

02:00:33.084 --> 02:00:33.459
Why?
